3361, "(fr)!html Alright pilots, listen up. Neither the PVD Frontière or Minister Khonsu II's transport made it to the staging area. We have reason to believe that Hammer of Light moles onboard each craft commandeered the ships. There is little doubt that Khonsu and the Frontière's crew are being held as ransom for Ozymandias, the Cardinal and it's crew."
