3364, "(fr)!html The location of the Frontière and it's crew is uncertain. However, the Admiral expects that the HoL wants this to be a very visible operation. We've narrowed down the list of locations and we suspect the Frontière is being held at the abandoned <span class='white'>Detiula Station<$slashspan>. While abandoned, the station is a well known landmark. Any engagement, success or failure, will surely be noticed."
3366, "(fr)!html We do have a positive ID on Khonsu II's transponder near the Ribos jump corridor. There is little doubt that the HoL knows about the transponder and are expecting us to carry out a counter operation. However, we cannot let the HoL move the <span class='blue'>Minister<$slashspan> out of Antarès. Khonsu is currently a political icon and his captivity could mean any number of fates for the Vasudan government."
3367, "Nœud de Saut de Ribos"
3368, "(fr)!html This operation may be straightforward, but it is also an extremely difficult situation. We have three priority targets in a single system with limited forces engaging and unknown number of hostiles. We expect that the Hammer of Light is also making use of their criminal and smuggler allies in order to retake the Cardinal. Unfortunately, we simply do not have time to go after each target individually."
3369, "(fr)!html The PVN is still reeling with the disappearance of the PVD Frontière. The only help they can provide is a few cruisers to supplement the guard around the Cardinal until reinforcements arrive from Vasuda. Parliament regrets that they cannot go after Khonsu themselves but given the circumstances, there's nothing they could do. So we are sending our own force.

Alpha, you will jump to the Ribos node, intercept <span class='white'>Khonsu's transport<$slashspan>, and secure the area."
3370, "(fr)!html When you arrive, your scanners will attempt to match and verify Khonsu's transponder signal. You must keep it from departing through the Ribos node. You may need to disable the transport. When that's complete, a boarding party will arrive, dock with the transport, and secure Khonsu. You are to take any and all measures necessary in order to bring the <span class='blue'>Minister<$slashspan> home."
