3541, "(fr)!html Alpha, we are relieved you made it back safely. Unfortunately, there was nothing more you could do. Ozymandias and his growing fleet are moving through the system attacking any target of opportunity. It is clear now that the <span class='green italic'>Rakyat<$slashspan> was bait to lure the whole of <span class='blue'>Bravo Group<$slashspan> into the field.

