3533, "(fr)!html <div class='blue'>GTD Intrépide<br$slash>Antarès System<br$slash>2336/11/22<$slashdiv>

<span class='blue'>New Technology: GTW Subach HL-7<$slashspan>

We have received a shipment of the new Subach HL-7 weapon. This new weapon fires highly focused x-ray beams and works superbly against shields of all varieties as well as hull plating. It is expensive to manufacture, but expected to quickly become standard issue for Terran pilots. This new weapon should provide a better damage to energy ratio over the standard Avenger Cannon. The stock is limited, so use at your discretion."
3534, "(fr)!html Pilots, we've got an emergency situation with one of our fleet patrols. The <span class='green italic'>GTC Rakyat<$slashspan>, a Leviathan class cruiser, was en route to rendezvous with <span class='blue'>cruiser group Bravo<$slashspan> when it was attacked by Hammer of Light forces, and left stranded. With Ozymandias now in control of <span class='white'>two destroyers and nearly a dozen light cruisers<$slashspan>, we don't have much time. The <span class='green italic'>Rakyat<$slashspan> reported structural damage to the internal reactor and engine systems. They have requested additional personnel and supplies to complete the repair and get underway as quickly as possible."
3535, "Rakyat"
