4230, "(fr)!html However, we paid a price for this victory. There is little left of our battlegroup and the local government is seeking sanctions against Admiral Po and the GTA. We have little choice but to leave the system in Federation control. The Antarès Federation have agreed to sign a non-aggression act with the GTA on the condition that GTD Intrépide is reassigned. GTA Command has ordered our battle group to Delta Serpentis pending an investigation into the events that occurred here in Antarès. Leaving Antarès in the hands of the Federation was a far greater option than surrendering the system to the Hammer of Light. This is a victory, pilot, however bittersweet."
