4223, "(fr)!html Ozymandias smells blood and thinks he's coming in to finish us off. We need to surprise him as rudely as he surprised us at Novograd. The genuine direness of our situation works in his favor as much as it does ours, because Ozymandias will be more likely to stick around to ensure a kill. Ozymandias' eagerness will be his undoing, if Admiral Po has planned this right."
