5268, "(fr)!html There was nothing you could have done to save the Intrépide. We were entirely unprepared for the level of defense that the Hammer of Light showed. GTA Command was following Admiral Khu's leadership. This was his plan and some of us feel his pride clouded his judgement. We have filed complaints through official channels with <span class='blue'>Parliament<$slashspan>, but there is nothing more we can do but mourn our dead.

