For those pilots of the Cutthroats previously stationed on the Intrépide, welcome aboard the Nereid. My name is <span class='white'>Captain Varner<$slashspan>. I wish it were under better circumstances and I offer condolences on the loss of your friends aboard the Intrépide. Unfortunately, your stay here will be short. We barely have the resources to accommodate our own squadrons, so you'll be dropped off in Delta Serpentis for reassignment.

