5382, "(fr)!html We've designated the installation Wayfarer Station, and she'll be our home in Luyten. As an old GTI site, she should be pretty cushy by military standards, but the LNA work crews report that many of the amenities have wandered off since the station was abandoned. Our freighters are mostly loaded out with ammunition, your fighters, and spare parts, but the LNA's&nbsp$semicolonAmanu Station has indicated a willingness to accept our requisition orders. Even so, let's not overdo it. The last thing we want to do is convince the anti-GTA factions within the LNA that we're here to take advantage of them."
5383, "(fr)!html The bulk of our equipment is being carried by the Triton-class Reno, Tangier, and Okayama, including the fighters you aren't flying today and a <span class='green italic'>Centaur<$slashspan>-class support ship. The Chronos-class Baloris and Novak are loaded out with supplies for our cruisers, while the Poseidon-class Quartzon and Brimspark are carrying equipment and rations for Wayfarer Station. The latter also has a complement of Phideas drones on board for construction duties around the station. Lastly, the GTM Gregor is accompanying us to investigate reports of a Lucerta plague outbreak on one of the LNA habitats. Her medical staff will also be tracking your medical reports between missions. All of these ships must make it to Luyten."
