5594, "(fr)Well... yeah. They're all so into $quoterebuilding$quote and $quotestarting fresh$quote. I just can't buy it."
5595, "(fr)Why not, if I may ask?"
5596, "(fr)Are you shitting me? Look, the last seven years, we've had bug aliens from the ass end of the galaxy fuck up the Sol node and our own intel spooks decided they were onto something, our enemies-turned-allies got their homeworld slagged, and I've got business in Antarès that's gotten all kinds of complicated lately, if you catch my meaning."
