5598, "(fr)Hey, we ended the 14 Years War for good. Aren't $quoteenemies-turned-allies$quote something to be hopeful about, Astarte?"
5599, "(fr)Yeah... except the ones who still are our enemies. Who're supposed to be in the same system we're heading to. What about them?"
5600, "(fr)Still your tongue, Terran. Do not mistake --"
5601, "(fr)Be at peace, lieutenant. Old wounds run deep."
5602, "(fr)We may seem interchangeable to you. A tall alien with more spikes than a claw-beetle, a robotic voice on the comm. But I would remind you of the PVD Hope. Or should our relations instead be dominated by the Hades?"
5603, "(fr)Uh..."
5604, "(fr)To say nothing of the battle of Sahr. We hurt the fanatics as badly as they hurt us. Speaker Amasis believes we may have them routed in a few standard months."
5605, "(fr)I do not trust Amasis. With more preparation, Sahr would have fallen. A commander who had risen from the Ambassadors would have understood that necessity."
5606, "(fr)Do you still believe Khonsu displays those characteristics?"
5607, "(fr)Khonsu is a talented administrator. But his military experience is overstated. Had we lingered to $quoteprepare,$quote we would not have inflicted even the losses we had. Intrépide's sacrifice would have been in vain. Speaker Amasis had the correct analysis. The admiralty was right to listen."
5608, "(fr)Forgive me, but is he still titled Speaker, even with Parliament dissolved?"
5609, "(fr)He uses the title."
5610, "(fr)As much as I love hearing the ins and outs of Vasudan politics... Can we talk about what the HoL may or may not be up to? It's been three years since the Taweret disappeared from Altair. Command still hasn't said anything about it, so either they don't know anything, or they know everything and it's got them scared shitless."
5611, "(fr)Well... if you apply a Kashiwabara transformation in a static subspace field, you might get... no, probably not."
5612, "(fr)Mav, my friends back in Antarès mentioned something called... $quoteOh-foe-sis$quote the Hammer was looking for. Some kind of Shivan tech?"
5613, "(fr)Not Shivan, and that's classified."
5614, "(fr)Alex, if there's anything from your time with the Cutthroats you can tell us..."
5615, "(fr)...fine. But I want this off the record, and I'm not breaking any regs for you."
5616, "(fr)Oh, this is gonna be so good."
