5619, "(fr)Didn't your AF buddies tell you about the Iraklion corridor?"
5620, "(fr)We have friends in Antarès, Mav, not the Federation."
5621, "(fr)Is it a shiny new gun?"
5622, "(fr)No. Whatever it is, it's incomplete. Ozymandias had part of it, I think. The Alliance has the rest. Beyond that, we know it's big enough for the HoL to send their biggest, baddest destroyer to poke the hornet's nest, and a lot of Admiral Po's fleet paid the price for it. But it's not Shivan. I can neither confirm nor deny anything else I may or may not know about anything."
