5626, "(fr)Hey, Mav, I've been meaning to ask. What really happened in Antarès? You know me and Charon only signed on near the end. How'd Po... y'know... lose?"
5627, "(fr)It was complicated. Ozymandias played him from the very start. Even if we caught Ozy in the end, I think breaking up the Terran Bloc Treaty may have been his goal all along."
