5911, "(fr)!html Pilots, attend. Five days ago, Captain Varner dispatched priority alerts to Centaur Station advising them of the capabilities the raiders displayed during the Chicxulub incident. They haven't replied, so we did some digging. The <span class='blue'>intersystem relays<$slashspan> here in Luyten claims to be receiving routine telemetry from their counterparts in Laramis, Barnard's Star, and Wolf 359. However, analysis of these messages has revealed several abnormalities consistent with <span class='red'>intentional data tampering<$slashspan>. Our working theory is that our message has been blocked by a third party, and we've got two good guesses as to who."
