5949, "(fr)!html Welcome back to Luyten, pilots. While this operation was ultimately a failure, you did well in keeping our assets intact, avoiding any friendly fatalities, and bringing back information in spite of everything you were up against. The Gregor is going to be even busier than expected with radiation injuries from the Lavoisier's engine, but there's no way you could have been prepared for those subspace mines. The Lavoisier's crew is reportedly having a field day trying to figure those out."
