While our situation in Luyten is iffy, I do have some good news to report. The 508th recently conducted a series of reconnaissance flights to observe enemy movements throughout the system. One of these flights happened to catch the HLC Taweret repeating the stunt it pulled in Altair. Ensign Ramil has agreed to share a summary of our findings. When the ensign's presentation is complete, flight crews are to report to duty stations. Pilots, get some coffee if you need it, and then meet Commander Jers in briefing room 1 for your frag orders."
