6603, "(fr)!html Thank you for coming here on such short notice, Commander. What you're about to hear is classified <span class='white'>Level Rho<$slashspan>. Needless to say, it stays between you, me, and Commander Jers. Treat this op like any of the blank spots in your record from Antarès.

I've been in contact with a naval intelligence officer embedded within the LNA. Much like myself, this person is a former GTI officer who was cleared to return to active service. They have, shall we say, some familiarity with communication systems. We theorize that an old GTI backdoor in the relay network may allow us to get a message past the raiders' jamming in Laramis. Needless to say, the existence of this backdoor is highly sensitive information."
