7212, "(fr)During our research into the data captured by the teams that boarded the Gallaecia, we learned that the drones are constantly sending updates to each other. The datastream is full of flight data, current and planned trajectories, targets, and tactical requests to the drone network."
7222, "(fr)Okay, I'm going to generate a couple wings of drones. I want you to take them out as fast as you can."
