7219, "(fr)If you only have two drones in your FoV, the targeting sensor will lock on to each one once. After that, it will lock on to each one a second time with the remaining missiles in volley. Using this to your advantage means you can double or even quadruple tap targets in dual fire mode."
7218, "(fr)Good. Now, there are a few limits to be aware of. First, it can only target drones that are within the forward sensor's field of view. Second, it will initially only target a drone once per volley. Let me explain that."
