7621, "(fr)!html The gurus over at Amanu put their heads together with the STX Exploration researchers and came up with a long-range search algorithm to figure out where these INEDAM drones are being made. Wayfarer and Amanu have been working with a small fleet of LNA and STX science vessels to detect and triangulate the positions of energy surges that match the search parameters. As of 30 minutes ago, we got our first hit."
