7986, "(fr)!html We're glad you made it back safely. What you found down there is distressing, to say the least. We did not expect the manufacturing facility to be a mobile carrier. Nothing in the GTI archival plans for the INEDAM project suggested that such a design was in the blueprints. Of course, we're dealing with an advanced tactical AI here, which were outlawed for a reason. We're prioritizing your sensor data for the techs to analyze. We need whatever intel we can get about IN.E.D.A.M.01."
