8399, "(fr)The SDS hatch a plan to turn INEDAM's own weapons against it."
8400, "(fr)!html Alright, pilots, I'll start with the good news. Thanks to your efforts, we've managed to keep our rescue missions ahead of IN.E.D.A.M.01's rampage throughout Luyten. All the civilian habitats in that ship's projected flight path have been evacuated to Amanu Station or one of the LNA's&nbsp$semicolonElcanos. The bad news is that we're running out of time. We've got less than 48 hours before it hits Amanu itself, and we don't have anywhere else to go."
