;;tips.cfg
4779, "(fr)Some missions require you to think outside the box. If the obvious approach isn't working for you, maybe you can find another."
4780, "(fr)This mission doesn't have a hidden collectable, so you can skip it without missing out."
4781, "(fr)Most INEDAM primaries inflict high hull and subsystem damage, but low shield damage. Pay attention to your shields."
4782, "(fr)Raider drones have weak shields and no countermeasures. This makes them vulnerable to missiles of all types."
4783, "(fr)INEDAM's forces have very pronounced strengths and weaknesses. Learn what they are and adjust your tactics when facing them."
4784, "(fr)You can pause or restart a mission by pressing Escape."
4785, "(fr)You can replay missions in the simulator, accessible through the barracks."
4761, "(fr)Press $R$ to target a ship that's attacking you."
4762, "(fr)Press $U$ to target a ship, cargo, or sentry that can be scanned."
4763, "(fr)Press $G$ to target the nearest ship or turret attacking your target. This is an effective way to protect large ships."
4764, "(fr)Press $Alt-Y$ to target the last ship to send a transmission. This is useful when your wingmates call for help."
4765, "(fr)Press F1 anywhere to get context-sensitive help. In the main hall, right-clicking will show clickable areas."
4766, "(fr)Press F3 in a mission to view and assign targeting hotkeys to individual ships."
4767, "(fr)Press F4 in a mission to view a backlog of all messages and ship kills."
4768, "(fr)There's something hidden in each main campaign mission. Find each one to unlock a unique ship."
4769, "(fr)Check the system viewer regularly. It updates after each mission."
4770, "(fr)Press $H$ to target a hostile ship, or $Alt-H$ to enable auto-targeting."
4771, "(fr)If you need to break line of sight, use the Hastings Depot for cover. A transport or crate will also work in a pinch."
4772, "(fr)Armor panels are cheap and effective at slowing Kuk's bombers."
4773, "(fr)Sentries around Angel 1 can intercept bombs, but won't last long without support."
4774, "(fr)Defense Nodes are effective fire support, but can't defend themselves very well."
4775, "(fr)Disable as many transports as you can without taking too much damage. You can't stop all of them."
4776, "(fr)There are many ways through this mission. If you get stuck, look for another approach."
4777, "(fr)In your fighter's terminal, press Up or Down to view previous commands. Press Alt-Q to close it."
4778, "(fr)Your fighter's headlights can be toggled by pressing $Alt-Shift-Z$. They are particularly useful in dark or cloudy environments."
11407, "(fr)The Banshee is great at weakening bomber shields, but weak against hulls. Use another weapon to finish the job."
11408, "(fr)The Phoenix V can snipe bombers at range. It's also great at blowing up torpedo tubes on enemy warships."
