1869, "(fr)The Tempest dumbfire missile is the successor to the Fury and DustDevil. Designed to be smaller, the Tempest uses a more volatile explosive compound to allow for increased damage over the Fury. The Tempest has proven effective against enemy small craft and cruisers in testing, and large numbers are being manufactured for its future use as a standard issue weapon."
1870, "(fr)Hornet"
