2115, "(fr)Derived from the Serkr warhead, the Cyclops is an anti-cruiser bomb that will fully replace the Tsunami in service. GTA and PVN engineers managed to further simplify the Serkr's design, decreasing its cost per unit even further and allowing for full-scale production using the core fusion warhead of the Harbinger itself, allowing Cyclops production to be run on converted Harbinger manufacturing lines. The Cyclops is effective against destroyers as well as cruisers, and will remain in service for a long period of time."
