10664, "(fr)The Roc is a significant refit of the MX-50 heat-seeking weapon that has been in use since the early Terran-Vasudan War. Engineers at STX Exploration outposts in Luyten and Laramis tinkered with the outposts' supplies of spare MX-50s to produce a weapon far more effective against enemy shields than the original. With the Roc conversion process able to be applied to all MX-50 variants, it is only a matter of time before the Roc becomes one of the baseline weapons in the GTA and PVN."
1674, "(fr)Rockeye"
1106, "(fr)The Fang is the Vasudan counterpart to the Fury. Fired in dual bursts, the Fang is weaker per missile than the Fury, but fires at a faster rate. Like the Fury, the Fang is typically used in an assault role, or as a supplemental weapon against other strikecraft."
