11139, "(fr)Training Simulator SCS-1-D, Advanced Training."
11140, "(fr)!html Welcome to <span class='white'>Simulated Combat Session SCS-1-<span>Delta<$slashspan><$slashspan>. This simulator module is provided on an experimental basis and HAS NOT been approved by the Galactic Terran Alliance. In this module, you will fly a simulation of the GTF Loki reconnaissance fighter. The Loki was originally developed by the GTI's Hades Rebellion as a stealth fighter. While its stealth capability was $quotecracked$quote during the insurrection, its shrouded engines and low-emission jump drive make it an effective reconnaissance platform.

This module focuses on advanced flight systems. You will learn to break missile lock and to divert power between your weapons, shields, and engines. These power shunts are an invaluable skill while operating high-intensity fighters like the Valkyrie and Loki.

Commit to the simulation when ready."
